# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ⚠️  AUDIT REMINDER: RECORD ALL FILE OPERATIONS IN AUDIT_LOG.json
# 
# After ANY file operation (create, move, delete, update):
# 1. Add entry to AUDIT_LOG.json with timestamp, action, file path, reason
# 2. Commit both the change AND the audit log update together
# 
# Format:
#   {
#     "timestamp": "2026-04-01T20:30:00-05:00",
#     "action": "MOVED|DELETED|CREATED|UPDATED",
#     "file": "path/to/file",
#     "reason": "why this was done",
#     "performed_by": "who did it"
#   }
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

